										</tr>

										<tr style="font-size:11px">
											<td>Banks Name:</td>
											<td style="">
												<div style="border-bottom:1px solid lightgray; width:550px; margin-left:20px">
													<span style="margin-left:20px">Soneri , HBL and Meezan Bank
